Solution settings class

SolutionSettings.Rd

Solution settings class

Solution settings class

Details

Definition for the SolutionSettings class.

The argument to value should be a list with the following elements:

id

character identifier for theme or weight.

parameter

character name of parameter. Available options are: "status", "factor", or "goal".

type

character indicating if the parameter is for a theme or weight. Available options are: "theme" or "weight".

The argument to value should be a list with the following elements:

id

character identifier for theme or weight.

parameter

character name of parameter. Available options are: "status", "factor", or "goal".

value

numeric or logical value for new parameter.

type

character indicating if the parameter is for a theme or weight. Available options are: "theme" or "weight".

Public fields

theme_ids

character vector of identifiers for the themes.

weight_ids

character vector of identifiers for the weights.

themes

list of Theme objects.

weights

list of Weight objects.
